to know it accurately, times 10

00:11:56.860 --> 00:12:00.850
to the 16th, most important
to know the exponent there,

00:12:00.850 --> 00:12:01.350
joules.

00:12:04.010 --> 00:12:07.284
And it's also perhaps
interesting to translate this

00:12:07.284 --> 00:12:08.700
into the kind of
energy units that

00:12:08.700 --> 00:12:12.100
