00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:35.720
which is a lot of
kilowatt hours.

00:12:35.720 --> 00:12:38.390
An interesting comparison, is
the total power consumption

00:12:38.390 --> 00:12:41.040
of the world, which
turns out to be

00:12:41.040 --> 00:12:44.320
comparable to a kilograms
worth of things.

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:47.410
I looked things up
